summary: Eisen Platte Lite converted to use SevenBase
descriptionHtml:
Description:
Mesh conversion for SevenBase of [b]the lite version[/b] of R18Pn\'s Eisen Platte armor .

Requires:
[url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/11050]R18Pn 01 - Eisen Platte Armor[/url]
[url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/36992]SeveNBase custom FemaleBodyReplacer[/url]

Recommended:
[url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/15594]R18Pn 01 - Eisen Platte Armor texture upgrade[/url]

Notes:
Only the Lite armor and the boots have been converted (no gloves).
The Black version is not very good.
author: yabo
